	usage : 
	
	just create a div like <div id="myGiantCursor"></div>
	and add these codes between the <head></head> of the page
	
	<script>
		$(function(){
			$('#myGiantCursor').giantCursor();
		});
	</script>
	
	options could be changed like :
	
	<script>
		$(function(){
			$('#myGiantCursor').giantCursor({
				cursorUrl 	: 'http://myCursorURL', // giant cursor image's url
				width  		: '48px',	// giant cursor's width
				height 		: '48px',	// giant cursor's height
				hideOriginal: true,		// if true, hides the original cursor of your borwser or OS
				top			: 0,		// giant cursor's top
				left		: -12,		// giant cursor's left
				blink		: true		// if true, the giant cursor blinks
			});
		});
	</script>
	
	
	
	have fun.. :]